{"tid":1298340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我重申一次 蘋果acc可以多個devices同時登入使用","createTime":"2019-07-09T00:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T01:03:26.000Z","uid":102798,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e0cfc223132361e0c1d3e79cf85f80f584b2dfd","tid":1298340,"uid":102798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:31:38.000Z","msg":"我知咁做係好仆街 但係燃眉之急可以幫老豆老母轉左先<br />\n首先你要一個用電話登記既蘋果acc （email登記既唔知得唔得 我未試）<br />\n是咁的 同老母搭巴士途中。。。<br />\n老母：e？ 點解我睇唔到蘋果既？<br />\n我：呀。。。唔記得幫你整tim<br />\n當時手上無電腦 電話開web又上過唒蘋果網 會有cache cookies 嫌麻煩諗住返屋企先幫佢課金 跟住就用老母電話login自己acc<br />\n然後就收到msg 打返嗰個4數字 done!<br />\n利申：最後返到屋企幫左老母課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後。。未課嗰班 咪撚咁度縮呀！ 咪撚同我講新聞無價呢啲垃鳩圾說話！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次開po<br />\n sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"945ce842e6b38a38b6d5753ff04264da4e74886f","tid":1298340,"uid":102798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:31:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce9d9bb8cf85cdd7d6e55561f88bcc66e17869c2","tid":1298340,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:32:21.000Z","msg":"課啦"},{"pid":"32b05f13a798bb500de208d6ca1ea0f1bc5ddd43","tid":1298340,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:32:43.000Z","msg":"港共成功左 由得我地和平遊行<br />\n<br />\n你地開始玩膠，即係證明你地不再憤怒，覺得好開心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298176</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca07ac9405592707dddafd1b34f3c5d53c645a63","tid":1298340,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:32:48.000Z","msg":"好撚叻呀<br />\n<br />\n大智慧慳錢錢呀中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2c368627d3e829d1c08f482438cfcf58b410c9","tid":1298340,"uid":102798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl